:: Hallways Encounter
<<set $outside to 0>><<set $location to "school">><<schooleffects>><<effects>>

<<cleareventpool>>

/* Okay, so the math here is a bit complex, so let me summarize the intended outcomes of the event weightings:
	 fame.sex from 0-399 (unknown through known), 	NPC has a 1 in 6 chance (16%) of asking for sex
	 fame.sex from 400-599 (all of recognised), 	NPC has a 2 in 7 chance (28%) of asking for sex
	 fame.sex from 600-800 (lower half of famous), 	NPC has a 3 in 8 chance (37%) of asking for sex
	 fame.sex from 800-999 (upper half of famous),	NPC has a 4 in 9 chance (44%) of asking for sex
	 fame.sex from 1000 or more (all of notorious), 	NPC has a 5 in 10 chance (50%%) of asking for sex
   In conclusion, the more of a known slut the PC is, the more NPCs will attempt to proposition them */
<<set _propositionWeight to $fame.sex gte 200 ? Math.floor($fame.sex / 200) lte 5 ? Math.floor($fame.sex / 200) : 5 : 1>>
<<addinlineevent "encounter_proposition" _propositionWeight>>
	당신은 잡담한다. 그는 좋은 사람처럼 보이나, 당신이 떠나려고 몸을 돌리자 당신의 팔을 붙잡는다. "아무도 방해하지 못할 장소를 알고 있어."
	<<if $schoolrep.herm gte 5>>
		그는 당신의 몸을 눈으로 훑다가 가랑이 쪽으로 시선을 보낸다. "네가 특별하다는 걸 들었어."
	<<elseif $schoolrep.crossdress gte 5 and isCrossdressing()>>
		그는 당신의 몸을 눈으로 훑다가 가랑이 쪽으로 시선을 보낸다. "네게 비밀이 있다고도 들었어."
	<<else>>
		그는 당신의 몸을 눈으로 훑는다.
	<</if>>
	<br><br>

	<<if hasSexStat("promiscuity", 2)>>
		<<link [[받아들인다|Hallways Encounter Sex]]>><<set $sexstart to 1>><</link>><<promiscuous2>>
		<br>
	<<else>>
		당신은 그의 제안을 수락할 만큼 음란하지 않다.
		<br>
	<</if>>
	<<link [[거절한다|Hallways]]>><<endevent>><<set $eventskip to 1>><</link>>
	<br>
<</addinlineevent>>

<<addinlineevent "encounter_chat" 5>>
	당신은 잡담한다. 그는 좋은 사람처럼 보인다.
	<br><br>

	<<link [[다음|Hallways]]>><<endevent>><<set $eventskip to 1>><</link>>
	<br>
<</addinlineevent>>

